{
  "texts": [
    "AI techniques leveraged in disinformation campaigns can be grouped into a few broad categories:",
    "Generative AI for content creation -this includes deepfakes (AI-generated synthetic video or audio that imitates real people) and AI-generated text (using large language models).",
    "These tools can fabricate convincing false content at scale.",
    "Synthetic identities and personas -AI can create realistic profile pictures, names, and personal backgrounds, enabling the mass production of fictitious online personas that appear authentic.",
    "Automation and bot networks -AI-driven bots can mimic human behavior on social media, posting and engaging with content automatically."
  ]
}